data.description: UPDATES AND CUSTOM TOUCHES GALORE!!! This GORGEOUS 3 bedroom, 2 bath Showcase home was built in 2004 and is located in the Westgate neighborhood on LAKE EUSTIS!! As soon as you drive up you will notice the stunning curb appeal of the home, with the updated dark gray exterior paint, copper accents including downspouts and garage lights, along with the custom made shutters(all updated less than 4 years ago).  The beautiful front door was recently replaced adding to the homes charm. Upon entering the home, you will immediately be drawn to the vaulted ceilings and OPEN feel of the layout. The large great room boasts a double set of sliding glass doors that lead out to your SCREENED in LANAI. The lanai also features a custom built bar and outdoor SPEAKERS wired for indoor/outdoor use that connect to your Bluetooth enabling you to play your favorite music while grilling or entertaining family and friends!  The home has NEW laminate flooring throughout the main living areas and all 3 bedrooms. The interior of the home has recently been painted and new ceiling fans, lighting and door handles on all interior doors installed. The SPACIOUS kitchen has been UPDATED with all new appliances, including a Samsung Bespoke refrigerator that has removable glass panels to customize with your favorite colors! (all less than a year old)  A CUSTOM epoxy countertop in the kitchen along with open shelving against a stunning brick wall make this kitchen very warm and inviting! Both bathrooms in the home have been UPDATED with beautiful CUSTOM countertops, all NEW modern lighting and mirrors. The spacious owner's suite features vaulted ceilings and sliding glass doors out to the screened lanai.  You will also LOVE the convenience of the HUGE WALK- IN closet and split DUAL vanities featured in the main ensuite, as well as a private water closet and linen closet. The laundry room has convenient access from the garage and includes a utility sink and WASHER and DRYER(less than a year old). When it's time to relax, head out to the backyard oasis where you can take in the sights and sounds of nature with the mature trees and butterfly garden. Or head out on the lake, just bring your boat and fishing poles and take advantage of the COMMUNITY DOCK! If you are looking for a home where you can entertain and unwind then this is the home for YOU! Don't delay, call me TODAY for a showing! Listing agent is also owner of the property.
